#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:10
msgid "int"
msgstr "int"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:12
msgid "Integer built-in type."
msgstr "整型内置类型。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:15
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:17
msgid "Signed 64-bit integer type."
msgstr "有符号的64位整数类型。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:19
msgid ""
"It can take values in the interval ``[-2^63, 2^63 - 1]``, i.e. "
"``[-9223372036854775808, 9223372036854775807]``. Exceeding those bounds "
"will wrap around."
msgstr ""
"它的取值范围为区间 ``[-2^63, 2^63 - 1]``，即 ``[-9223372036854775808, "
"9223372036854775807]``。超出这些界限将环绕。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:21
msgid ""
"``int`` is a :ref:`Variant <class_Variant>` type, and will thus be used "
"when assigning an integer value to a :ref:`Variant <class_Variant>`. It "
"can also be enforced with the ``: int`` type hint."
msgstr ""
"``int`` 是一种 :ref:`Variant <class_Variant>` 类型，因此在将整数值赋给 :ref:`Variant "
"<class_Variant>` 时使用。也可以使用 ``: int`` 类型提示来强制类型。"

