#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:54
msgid ""
"Cast a :ref:`bool <class_bool>` value to an integer value, ``int(true)`` "
"will be equals to 1 and ``int(false)`` will be equals to 0."
msgstr ""
"将 :ref:`bool <class_bool>` 值强制转换为整数值，``int(true)`` 将等于1，而 ``int(false)`` "
"将等于0。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:58
msgid ":ref:`int <class_int>` **int** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` from **)**"
msgstr ":ref:`int <class_int>` **int** **(** :ref:`float <class_float>` from **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:60
msgid ""
"Cast a float value to an integer value, this method simply removes the "
"number fractions, so for example ``int(2.7)`` will be equals to 2, "
"``int(.1)`` will be equals to 0 and ``int(-2.7)`` will be equals to -2."
msgstr ""
"将浮点值强制转换为整数值，此方法只删除数字分数部分，因此例如 ``int(2.7)`` 将等于2，``int(.1)`` 将等于0，而 "
"``int(-2.7)`` 等于-2。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:64
msgid ""
":ref:`int <class_int>` **int** **(** :ref:`String <class_String>` from "
"**)**"
msgstr ""
":ref:`int <class_int>` **int** **(** :ref:`String <class_String>` from "
"**)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_int.rst:66
msgid ""
"Cast a :ref:`String <class_String>` value to an integer value, this "
"method is an integer parser from a string, so calling this method with an"
" invalid integer string will return 0, a valid string will be something "
"like ``'1.7'``. This method will ignore all non-number characters, so "
"calling ``int('1e3')`` will return 13."
msgstr ""
"将 :ref:`String <class_String>` "
"值转换为整数值，此方法是字符串的整数解析器，因此使用无效的整数字符串调用此方法将返回0，有效的字符串将类似于 "
"``'1.7'``。此方法将忽略所有非数字字符，因此调用 ``int('1e3')`` 将返回13。"

